data.description: $15,000 Seller Concessions! Welcome Home! This one-of-a-kind property features Owned Solar, Newer roof, newer gutters and private swimming pool. This home has 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, family and living rooms. A spacious bonus room with separate front entrance could be used as a home office or guest quarters. A large open concept kitchen with new refrigerator, new reverse osmosis filtration system and new freezer. Easy access to the formal dining room, family room and the back patio. The backyard highlights in ground swimming pool, detached oversized one car garage, stamped concrete, dog run and a fire pit. This property is conveniently located near the city park, shopping, airport.
